Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.33, sn,, 0000,0000,0000,, Buddhovo oko ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.90, sn,, 0000,0000,0000,, Je to tvoje vina.  Je to kvůli tobě.
